### Animation Keyframes:

```css
@keyframes blob {
  0% {
    transform: scale(1) translate(0px, 0px);
  }
  33% {
    transform: scale(1.1) translate(30px, -50px);
  }
  66% {
    transform: scale(0.9) translate(-20px, 20px);
  }
  100% {
    transform: scale(1) translate(0px, 0px);
  }
}

.animate-blob {
  animation: blob 15s infinite ease-in-out;
}
```

### MUST DO:

- **ALWAYS** use blob animations for background elements
- **ALWAYS** apply smooth transitions (duration-300)
- **ALWAYS** use proper z-index layering (-z-10 for backgrounds)
- **ALWAYS** maintain consistent animation timing

### NEVER DO:

- ‚ùå Create jarring or abrupt animations
- ‚ùå Use animations that interfere with readability
- ‚ùå Overuse animations to the point of distraction

